Summary: Object seen in a photo taken with a digital camera
divs: Sighting DetailsThe incident was pretty much instant, i took a picture of a lovely sunset while on holiday in cuba. Immediately on taking the picture i noticed on the view screen an object which i had not seen in the sky. i looked up and still there was nothing there. I took a few more pictures of the same area but nothing else appeared on the screen. I dont know what is on the picture but im sure you'll admit there is definately something wierd there
